### Check Working On Local Host

- Open CMD ( or in case Anaconda Anaconda Prompt - in case of Anacodonda Standard CMD is alsow avaliable )
- Go to script folder: cd.. 
- Run Script:
   * PathWithFolder>   python app.py                             <- In case Of 'Anaconda Prompt' or standard Python installation
   * PathWithFolder>   PathToPythonExecFile\\python.exe app.py   <- In case of Using Anaconda and standard CMD. 
                                                                   # find phyton.exe file in spyder:
								        import sys
								        sys.executable
								        
								      Example of PathToPythonExecFile: C:\\Users\\kamil\\anaconda3\\python.exe
- Check web site on the browser
    http://localhost:8050
    http://localhost:3000
- kill
   ctr+c+c <- 2 times
    
